high_descs: Turn around then turn right to face the counter with a toaster.
Pick up the spatula from the counter.
Turn around, go straight, and then turn right to face the sink.
Clean the spatula in the sink.
Turn around then turn left to face the oven.
Put the spatula in the drawer of the counter, beneath the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean spatula in the drawer.

high_descs: turn left and walk forwards to the kitchen counter
grab the knife off of the counter which is behind the spoon
turn around and walk over to the kitchen sink on the right side of the room
rinse off the spatula inside the sink, then pick it back up
turn around and walk over to the right side of the kitchen stove on the left but, stay backed up just a bit so you can use the pull out drawer
place the spatula inside of the pull out drawer to the right of the stove
anns.task_desc: place the spatula inside of the pull out drawer to the right of the stove

high_descs: Turn to your left and face the counter
Grab the spatula off of the counter
Turn left and head to the sink
Place the spatula in the sink and wash it. Grab the spatula out of the sink.
Turn around and head back to the counter
Open the top drawer underneath the counter and place the spatula inside. Close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Putting the spatula in the drawer
